title: Catherine Coulter-Eleventh Hour
description:
In their seventh crime swoop, FBI agents Lacey Sherlock and Dillon Savich 
track down a very elusive murderer. Father Michael Joseph, the twin brother of 
a FBI colleague, is slain, but the only witness to the crime vanishes. To the 
double mystery of murder and disappearance is quickly added a third element: 
Sherlock and Savich discover a connection between Father Michael's killing and 
one "committed" on an upcoming episode of a trendy new TV series. Is the 
murderer a copycat killer or a psychic?
